WEBVTT

00:03:00.480 --> 00:03:02.936
And now Canada is taking even more.

00:03:02.960 --> 00:03:04.816
And yet, if you ask Canadians

00:03:04.840 --> 00:03:07.496
what makes them proudest of their country,

00:03:07.520 --> 00:03:09.976
they rank "multiculturalism,"

00:03:10.000 --> 00:03:12.216
a dirty word in most places,

00:03:12.240 --> 00:03:13.456
second,

00:03:13.480 --> 00:03:15.040
ahead of hockey.

00:03:15.720 --> 00:03:16.936
Hockey.

00:03:16.960 --> 00:03:19.000
(Laughter)

00:03:19.960 --> 00:03:22.136
In other words,
at a time when other countries

00:03:22.160 --> 00:03:25.416
are now frantically building
new barriers to keep foreigners out,

00:03:25.440 --> 00:03:28.320
Canadians want even more of them in.

00:03:29.320 --> 00:03:31.496
Now, here's the really interesting part.